ant solution for WordPress.","plural":null,"translations":["Webov\u00e9 str\u00e1nky, zam\u011b\u0159en\u00e9 na u\u017eivatele z EU, kter\u00e9 nastavuj\u00ed jin\u00e9 ne\u017e nezbytn\u00e9 soubory cookie, pot\u0159ebuj\u00ed banner s mo\u017enost\u00ed souhlasu s pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1n\u00edm soubor\u016f cookie. Doporu\u010dujeme Real Cookie Banner jako \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed pro WordPress, kter\u00e9 je v souladu se z\u00e1sadami ePrivacy a GDPR."],"translator_comments":"","extracted_comments":"","references":[],"flags":[]},"You can move or insert a post or page directly into a category without having to deal with checkboxes.":{"is_plural":false,"context":null,"singular":"You can move or insert a post or page directly into a category without having to deal with checkboxes.","plural":null,"translations":["P\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvek nebo str\u00e1nku m\u016f\u017eete p\u0159esunout nebo vlo\u017eit p\u0159\u00edmo do kategorie, ani\u017e byste se museli zaob\u00edrat za\u0161krt\u00e1vac\u00edmi pol\u00ed\u010dky."],"translator_comments":"","extracted_comments":"","references":[],"flags":[]},"Your WordPress site will certainly continue to grow. Organize your media library with folders!":{"is_plural":false,"context":null,"singular":"Your WordPress site will certainly continue to grow. Organize your media library with folders!","plural":null,"translations":["Va\u0161e str\u00e1nky WordPress budou ur\u010dit\u011b d\u00e1le r\u016fst. Zorganizujte svou multimedi\u00e1ln\u00ed knihovnu pomoc\u00ed slo\u017eek!"],"translator_comments":"","extracted_comments":"","references":[],"flags":[]},"Your uploads can say more than a thousand words. Unfortunately, search engines do not understand the content of images, for example. Organize your uploads directly in meaningful folder names and achieve a better ranking in search engines!":{"is_plural":false,"context":null,"singular":"Your uploads can say more than a thousand words. Unfortunately, search engines do not understand the content of images, for example. Organize your uploads directly in meaningful folder names and achieve a better ranking in search engines!","plural":null,"translations":["Va\u0161e p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky mohou \u0159\u00edct v\u00edce ne\u017e tis\u00edc slov. Vyhled\u00e1va\u010de bohu\u017eel nerozum\u00ed nap\u0159\u00edklad obsahu obr\u00e1zk\u016f. Uspo\u0159\u00e1dejte sv\u00e9 nahran\u00e9 soubory p\u0159\u00edmo do v\u00fdsti\u017en\u00fdch n\u00e1zv\u016f slo\u017eek a dos\u00e1hn\u011bte lep\u0161\u00edho um\u00edst\u011bn\u00ed ve vyhled\u00e1va\u010d\u00edch!"],"translator_comments":"","extracted_comments":"","references":[],"flags":[]},"cookie-banner-frontend.png":{"is_plural":false,"context":null,"singular":"cookie-banner-frontend.png","plural":null,"translations":["cookie-banner-frontend.png"],"translator_comments":"","extracted_comments":"","references":[],"flags":[]},"https:\/\/devowl.io\/go\/real-cookie-banner?source=cross-rcb":{"is_plural":false,"context":null,"singular":"https:\/\/devowl.io\/go\/real-cookie-banner?source=cross-rcb","plural":null,"translations":["https:\/\/devowl.io\/go\/real-cookie-banner?source=cross-rcb"],"translator_comments":"","extracted_comments":"","references":[],"flags":[]}},"headers":{"Project-Id-Version":"n\/a","Report-Msgid-Bugs-To":"","PO-Revision-Date":"2024-04-25 12:39+0000","Last-Translator":"Matthias G\u00fcnter <matthias.guenter@devowl.io>","Language-Team":"Czech <https:\/\/translate.devowl.io\/projects\/devowl-wp-real-utils-backend-php\/develop\/cs\/>","Language":"cs_CZ","MIME-Version":"1.0","Content-Type":"text\/plain; charset=UTF-8","Content-Transfer-Encoding":"8bit","Plural-Forms":"nplurals=3; plural=(n==1) ? 0 : (n>=2 && n<=4) ? 1 : 2;","X-Generator":"Weblate 5.4.3"}}